sections.text:
81-1314.Delegation of authority.

Any official named in sections 81-1301 to 81-1317 shall have the power to delegate authority for execution of responsibilities under sections 81-1301 to 81-1317 to any person such official may designate.

SourceLaws 1967, c. 573, ยง 14, p. 1896.
